<h3 id="post-scheduled-limit-change">POST Scheduled Limit Change</h3>

<p>Create a new scheduled limit change for a service binding</p>
<pre class="highlight shell"><code>curl <span class="s2">"https://example.com/api/bindings/540f43bc-b9cc-4126-97a4-a56b64052da4/scheduled_limit_changes"</span> <span class="se">\ </span>
    -X POST <span class="se">\ </span>
    -H <span class="s2">"Authorization: Bearer UAA_ACCESS_TOKEN"</span> <span class="se">\ </span>
    -d <span class="s1">'{
  "executes_at": "2021-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "min_instances": 2,
  "max_instances": 5,
  "recurrence": 1,
  "enabled": true
}'</span>
</code></pre>
<pre class="highlight plaintext"><code>Example Response
</code></pre>
<pre class="highlight http"><code><span class="k">HTTP</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="m">1.1</span> <span class="m">200</span> <span class="ne">OK</span>
<span class="s">{</span>
<span class="s">  "guid": "33877394-8de7-4a7b-56ae-8eca87d0d469",</span>
<span class="s">  "created_at": "2021-01-01T00:00:00Z",</span>
<span class="s">  "updated_at": "2021-01-01T00:00:00Z",</span>
<span class="s">  "executes_at": "2016-12-25T02:00:00Z",</span>
<span class="s">  "min_instances": 1,</span>
<span class="s">  "max_instances": 2,</span>
<span class="s">  "service_binding_guid": "540f43bc-b9cc-4126-97a4-a56b64052da4",</span>
<span class="s">  "recurrence": 64,</span>
<span class="s">  "enabled": true</span>
<span class="s">}</span>
</code></pre>

<h4 id="http-request">HTTP Request</h4>

<p><code class="prettyprint">POST /api/bindings/{binding_guid}/scheduled_limit_changes</code></p>

<h4 id="uri-parameters">URI Parameters</h4>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Example</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>binding_guid</td>
<td><code class="prettyprint">string</code> (required)</td>
<td><code class="prettyprint">540f43bc-b9cc-4126-97a4-a56b64052da4</code></td>
<td>GUID of the service binding</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
